#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:0
msgid "﻿# UB Overflow 问题排查指南"
msgstr "# UB Overflow Troubleshooting Guide"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:2
msgid "## 概述"
msgstr "## Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:4
msgid "UB Overflow 是 Triton-Ascend 开发中常见的问题。本文档详细介绍 UB Overflow 的常见原因、解决方案和调试方法。"
msgstr "UB Overflow is a common issue in Triton-Ascend development. This document provides a detailed overview of the common causes, solutions, and debugging methods for UB Overflow."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:6
msgid "## 常见原因及解决方案"
msgstr "## Common Causes and Solutions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:8
msgid "### 1. 使用了会增加 UB 开销的接口参数"
msgstr "### 1. Using interface parameters that increase UB overhead"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:10
msgid "某些接口在特定参数配置下会自动添加额外的处理逻辑，导致 UB 空间使用增加："
msgstr "Some interfaces automatically add additional processing logic under specific parameter configurations, resulting in increased UB space usage."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:12
msgid "#### `tl.maximum`、`tl.minimum`、`tl.clamp` 接口的 `propagate_nan` 参数"
msgstr "#### The `propagate_nan` parameter of the `tl.maximum`, `tl.minimum`, and `tl.clamp` interfaces"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:14
msgid ""
"**问题描述：**\n"
"当设置 `propagate_nan=tl.PropagateNAN.NONE` 时，系统会自动添加 NaN 值检测和处理逻辑。\n"
msgstr ""
"**Problem Description:**  \n"
"When `propagate_nan=tl.PropagateNAN.NONE` is set, the system automatically adds NaN value detection and handling logic.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:16
msgid "**影响：**"
msgstr "**Impact:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:18
msgid ""
"- 显著增加 UB 空间使用\n"
"- 可能导致性能下降\n"
msgstr ""
"- Significantly increases UB space usage\n"
"- May lead to performance degradation\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:22
msgid ""
"- 如果输入数据不包含 NaN 值或不需要严格的 NaN 处理语义，考虑调整 `propagate_nan` 参数值\n"
"- 在 UB 空间紧张的场景下，优先选择不会触发额外 NaN 处理的参数配置\n"
msgstr ""
"- If the input data does not contain NaN values or does not require strict NaN handling semantics, consider adjusting the `propagate_nan` parameter value\n"
"- In scenarios where UB space is constrained, prioritize parameter configurations that do not trigger additional NaN handling\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:24
msgid "### 2. 中间变量过多"
msgstr "### 2. Excessive intermediate variables"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:26
msgid ""
"**问题：**\n"
"kernel 中定义了大量临时张量或中间计算结果\n"
msgstr ""
"**Problem:**  \n"
"A large number of temporary tensors or intermediate computation results are defined in the kernel.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:30
msgid ""
"- 减少不必要的中间变量\n"
"- 复用已分配的缓冲区\n"
"- 将大计算拆分为多个小 kernel\n"
msgstr ""
"- Reduce unnecessary intermediate variables  \n"
"- Reuse allocated buffers  \n"
"- Split large computations into multiple small kernels\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:32
msgid "### 3. shape 过大"
msgstr "### 3. shape too large"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:34
msgid ""
"**问题：**\n"
"处理高维/大 shape 张量\n"
msgstr ""
"**Problem:**  \n"
"Processing high-dimensional / large-shape tensors\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:36
msgid "**解决方案：**"
msgstr "**Solution:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:38
msgid ""
"- 考虑将大 tensor 分块处理\n"
"- 修改分块策略，减小每块的大小\n"
msgstr ""
"- Consider processing large tensors in blocks\n"
"- Modify the blocking strategy to reduce the size of each block\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:40
msgid "## 调试建议"
msgstr "## Debugging Suggestions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:42
msgid ""
"1. **开启详细日志**\n"
"   - 使用 `TRITON_DEBUG=1` 查看详细的编译信息\n"
"   - 定位具体哪个算子导致 UB 溢出\n"
msgstr ""
"1. **Enable Detailed Logging**\n"
"   - Use `TRITON_DEBUG=1` to view detailed compilation information\n"
"   - Identify which specific operator causes the UB overflow\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:44
msgid ""
"2. **逐步排查**\n"
"   - 通过注释掉部分代码，定位导致问题的具体操作\n"
msgstr ""
"2. **Step-by-Step Troubleshooting**\n"
"   - Locate the specific operation causing the issue by commenting out parts of the code.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:46
msgid ""
"3. **参考文档**\n"
"   - 查看各接口文档中的\"特殊限制说明\"部分\n"
"   - 了解可能增加 UB 开销的参数配置\n"
msgstr ""
"3. **Reference Documentation**\n"
"   - Check the \"Special Limitations\" section in each interface document\n"
"   - Understand parameter configurations that may increase UB overhead\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:48
msgid ""
"4. **优化策略**\n"
"   - 优先处理占用 UB 空间较大的算子\n"
"   - 考虑重新设计算法以减少中间变量\n"
"   - 考虑修改分块策略\n"
msgstr ""
"4. **Optimization Strategies**\n"
"   - Prioritize operators that occupy significant UB space\n"
"   - Consider redesigning algorithms to reduce intermediate variables\n"
"   - Consider modifying the tiling strategy\n"

#. type: blank
#: docs/zh/debug_guide/ub_overflow.md:49
msgid ""
